messages.content: ComfyUI-Panda3d is an extension or custom node for ComfyUI that integrates Panda3D game engine functionality into the ComfyUI framework.
What does the basic workflow example of ComfyUI-Panda3d demonstrate?
The basic workflow example demonstrates how to use ComfyUI-Panda3d to create a simple scene with a rotating panda model.
Where can the workflow JSON file for the basic example be found?
The workflow JSON file for the basic example can be found at https://github.com/chaojie/ComfyUI-Panda3d/blob/main/workflow.json.
Is there a visual representation of the basic workflow example available?
Yes, there is an image named 'wf_basic.png' that visually represents the basic workflow example.
What format is the video demonstration of the basic example in?
The video demonstration of the basic example is in GIF format.
How many examples are provided for ComfyUI-Panda3d?
The documentation provides 1 example for ComfyUI-Panda3d, which is the basic workflow example.
What is the file name of the video demonstrating the basic workflow example?
The file name of the video demonstrating the basic workflow example is 'video.gif'.
